1. User login to the app with the email id and password or if he/she is coming first time in the app then he/she will be clicking on the sign up button.
2.Then if he/she want to exchange an item to any one so he/she will give all the details in the form of exchange items.
3. Then when he/she click on the exchange button then the app will start finding a person who is satisfied with the deal.
4. When the person is found the app will show its details to the User and then bothe then person will contact each other and exchange their items.
5. if the User is new and clicks on the sign up button he have to enter all his details to the new User form only once. 
